org.openmap4u.builder

Class ImageBuilder<B extends ImageBuilder<B>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openmap4u.builder.ImageBuilder<B>
  • Type Parameters:
    B - The type of the image builder.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Buildable<ImageStyleable,B>, Drawable<ImageStyleable>, ImageDrawable, Plugable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Image

    public abstract class ImageBuilder<B extends ImageBuilder<B>>
extends Object
implements ImageDrawable
    All image builder plugins are derifed from this abstract base class. The protected methods can be exposed by the respective implementation of this abstract base template class.
    Author:
    Michael Hadrbolec
